    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119780/extras/f8fbb0014ed3decf30a00ea6215d2c5b.poster.avif?t=1760051485\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119780/extras/f8fbb0014ed3decf30a00ea6215d2c5b.webm?t=1760051485\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119780/extras/f8fbb0014ed3decf30a00ea6215d2c5b.mp4?t=1760051485\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏概念：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >模拟经营和扩展一家得来速商店，玩家在其中接收订单，准备各种饮料和食物，管理供应，并高效地服务客户。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏元素：<br><br>1. 接单：<br>- 接收并输入客户的饮料和食物订单。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119780/extras/54ca894ced5c59c50004b72737dcce81.poster.avif?t=1760051485\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119780/extras/54ca894ced5c59c50004b72737dcce81.webm?t=1760051485\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2. 准备：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 选择正确的杯子大小和形状来装饮料。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 按要求准备食物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119780/extras/b330effcdcd442573463dc8ff4c320c3.poster.avif?t=1760051485\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119780/extras/b330effcdcd442573463dc8ff4c320c3.webm?t=1760051485\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119780/extras/b330effcdcd442573463dc8ff4c320c3.mp4?t=1760051485\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3. 定制：<br>- 定制你的商店和价格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119780/extras/ba9b94b096ddfc86b5c743f938082364.poster.avif?t=1760051485\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119780/extras/ba9b94b096ddfc86b5c743f938082364.webm?t=1760051485\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119780/extras/ba9b94b096ddfc86b5c743f938082364.mp4?t=1760051485\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4. 支付系统：<br>- 使用现金、信用卡或移动支付处理付款。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 输入金额，提供正确的找零，并准确完成交易。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5. 供应管理：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   - 监控库存并补充供应，以保持商店库存充足。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119780/extras/3ab2e34c892851f07ec733d970c0fa2c.poster.avif?t=1760051485\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119780/extras/3ab2e34c892851f07ec733d970c0fa2c.webm?t=1760051485\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119780/extras/3ab2e34c892851f07ec733d970c0fa2c.mp4?t=1760051485\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6. 增长和扩展：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   - 通过升级设备、添加新菜单项和开设新店来改善和扩展商店。<br>- 明智地投资利润，以提升商店的声誉并吸引更多客户。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >目标：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >高效管理和发展得来速，准确完成订单，保持充足的供应，并为你的商店建立良好的声誉。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这款游戏提供了一个动态且现实的体验，模拟经营和扩展得来速，管理各种饮料和食物，处理多样的支付交易，并确保稳定的商品供应。</p>",
